Although whatever happened on the 20th of September 2015 was a miracle, we as a team cannot allow all the hard work in exploiting these hydro-meteorological model and the Vulnerability Index to not be used. Non-governmental organizations are in dire need of assistance in weather-risk management.
Respondents indicated that storms put in jeopardy the hard-won efforts of the entrepreneurs in the island. In the initial steps of the project, discussions were held with the Managing Partner of the Richelieu Hotel, which rains heavily compounded by large quantities of water and an intense wind, transformed the Chagos Reservoir, technically an off-plot water reservoir, into a river in a matter of minutes. The traveler who departs for the South-East Poineer of Mauritius would be left to wonder how this occurred, with the particular photographer engaging in detailing how the water entered through a house window within inches of the bed where he was sleeping. Similar accounts have been given for other properties on the River du Rempart. In a bid to seek help from the European Union on an off-plot disaster, the launching of a university has seen requests being recorded to grant any support, on request, through action funding plans. Further requests include the impression of an agrarian map and the analysis of data relating to the geology and morphology of the waterway from the reservoir to the river.
